          module:
          - rid: 1516066228257685531
          - rid: 1516066228257685532
          statUsed: 0
          output: 'Though this gamble might well earn us a visit from an Imperial
            Inquisitor, it is undeniable that the common folk are deeply enticed
            by subjects forbidden since the last Faith Eclipse. The mass is a triumph!

            [Gained
            20 Flock & 30 Zeal]

'
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 1516066228257685533
          statUsed: 0
          output: 'What a disaster! The populace flees in terror at the mere prospect
            of being implicated in an Imperial Inquisition witch-hunt for harboring
            heretical knowledge. As for us? We had best sleep with one eye open.

            [Lost
            20 Zeal]

'
        - weight: 10
          module:
          - rid: 1516066228257685534
          - rid: 1516066228257685535
          statUsed: 5
          output: "Our profound and exhaustive knowledge concerning the ancient teachings\u2014now
            forbidden by the latest Faith Eclipse\u2014allows us to deliver an informative
            mass without ever falling into the peril of being branded as heretics.\r\n[Gained
            30 Flock & 60 Zeal]\r\n"
